<div class="fs-4">
  <h1 class="mb-4">Community Guidelines</h1>
	<p>
	  The Daddy App is <b>a safe space</b> where <b>you can be you</b>
		and where you can <b>talk about your children openly, shamelessly, and
		lovingly.</b>
	</p>
	<p>
	  You know, one of those "good vibes only" places.
	</p>
	<p>
		Don't be one who gets suspended or kicked off the app for saying or
		doing some dumb shit:
	</p>
	<div>
		<h4>👍 Do</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>Treat others as you would want to be treated</li>
			<li>Be tolerant towards other perspectives; respectfully disagree</li>
			<li>Respect the privacy and personal information of other dads</li>
			<li>Communicate courteously and respectfully</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div>
		<h4>👎 Do Not</h4>
		<ul>
				<li>Make personal attacks on other dads and/or their children</li>
				<li>Use defamatory remarks or make false statements</li>
				<li>Post prejudiced comments</li>
				<li>Bully or make inflammatory remarks</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
